<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Activation Lock</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .lock-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
            width: 350px;
        }
        .lock-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            color: #515154;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #d2d2d7;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #0071e3;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .help-link {
            color: #0071e3;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: block;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="lock-container">
        <div class="lock-icon">🔒</div>
        <h1>iPhone Locked By Apple</h1>
        <p>Our system has determined that this device may have been involved in illegal activities. Your iPhone has been locked.</p>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Blocked">
        <input type="password" placeholder="Blocked">
        <button class="button">Blocked</button>
        <a href="https://al-support.apple.com/#/" class="help-link">Think this is a mistake?</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
